                            <comment id="13011714" author="hudson" created="Sun, 27 Mar 2011 01:42:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in HBase-TRUNK #1816 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/HBase-TRUNK/1816/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/HBase-TRUNK/1816/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
