                            <comment id="13020497" author="v.himanshu" created="Sat, 16 Apr 2011 00:05:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A similar bug is there in ExecResult.write(DataOutput) when it is writing a null value, it throws a npe.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There should be a check that in case of null value one should use Writable else invoke .getClass().&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
